{"tid":1567822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日12點英領、3點銅鑼灣","createTime":"2019-09-14T07:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:34:58.000Z","uid":254330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"00753f89ef63e7e32e4400d7b749533a54987ea6","tid":1567822,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3wwXaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3wwXaK.jpg&h=72488e57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WoUZmCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWoUZmCs.jpg&h=e1eb5423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><em>915 915 915 915 915</em></ins></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">15 September </span></span><br />\n12點,英國領事館🇬🇧<br />\n12pm,British Consulate🇬🇧 (Nearby Admiralty Station)<br />\n3點,銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n3pm,East Point Road (Nearby Causeway Bay Station)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再講英國幫唔到手所以去黎冇用,英國作為《中英聯合聲明》嘅其中一個簽署國,佢係可以介入嘅。英國唔敢介入?你班仆街唔撚去make noise,冇番咁上下人數,點敢介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?你唔出黎都好意思話人唔介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?Freedom is not free!<br />\n英國有政治力量,美國有軍事力量,政府咁怕我地搵外國勢力,證明靠外國勢力可以揸實佢另外果粒春袋!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> God save our Queen <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> God save Hong Kong <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直落3點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要再次逼爆港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要嗌英文口號,唔好淨係得中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要比外國知道,香港人仲未放棄,唔會接受政府嘅條件,堅持五大訴求,缺一不可!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">FIVE Demands<br />\nNOT ONE LESS!</span><br />\n<br />\nFight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\nNo Rioters, Only Tyrannies!<br />\nHong Kong Police is Murderers!<br />\nNo China , Free Hong Kong!<br />\nDemocracy Now! Human Rights Now!<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong, Revolution of our times!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">FIVE Demands<br />\nNOT ONE LESS!<br />\n</span><br />\n915 港島見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求！缺一不可！</span>"},{"pid":"a63819ff5c94f07b232bc851fe75b4f295428750","tid":1567822,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13d3e0f5291a98cd93ed78db0e9d8bebdb6a2fc5","tid":1567822,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e817f73c7582c19748a50796da423a0701ba14f5","tid":1567822,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T07:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}